      • SimpleJson

        public SimpleJson(File file)
           throws IOException
        Create an object with the specified file to save. If already the file exists, create one by referencing the file.
        パラメータ:
        file - file to save
        例外:
        IOException - if a low-level I/O problem (unexpected end-of-input, network error) occurs (passed through as-is without additional wrapping -- note that this is one case where. (from Jackson's Javadoc)
